Title: On the Point-Splitting Method of the Commutator Anomaly of the Gauss Law

OperatorsAuthors: R. A. Bertlmann (Universitat Wien), Tomas Sykora (Charles University,

Prague)Comments: 16 pages, RevTex, 1 figure + 1 table, uses psbox.tex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D56 (1997) 2236-2241

We analyze the generalized point-splitting method and Jo's result for thecommutator anomaly. We find that certain classes of general regularizationkernels satisfying integral conditions provide a unique result, which, howeverdiffers from Faddeev's cohomological result.